Hello Anas,

I think you want to use the option &quot;source-tag-seeds&quot;. With that enabled, heritrix will record the seed that &quot;gave birth&quot; to each url in crawl.log, and will also produce an extra report called source-report.txt. In code, the source seed is available from a CrawlURI with curi.getString(CrawlURI.A_SOURCE_TAG).

Noah


